import React from 'react'
import { MdWorkOutline } from 'react-icons/fa'
import { WorkContainer, WorkInfoContainer, WorkImageContainer, WorkImageDiv, WorkImage } from './WorkElements'

const Work = () => {
  return (
    <WorkContainer>
      <WorkInfoContainer>
        <WorkImageContainer>
          <WorkImageDiv> 
            <WorkImage>
              <MdWorkOutline />
            </WorkImage>
          </WorkImageDiv>
        </WorkImageContainer>
      </WorkInfoContainer>
    </WorkContainer>
  )
}

export default Work
